---
---

<section class="section section-light">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="section-label">The Truth About AI</div>
    <h2>Most agencies don't need "AI everywhere."</h2>
    <div class="truth-content">
      <div class="truth-left fade-up">
        <p>They need AI in 3&ndash;5 places where time disappears daily:</p>
        <ul class="pain-list">
          <li>
            <div class="pain-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M14 2H6c-1.1 0-1.99.9-1.99 2L4 20c0 1.1.89 2 1.99 2H18c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V8l-6-6zm2 16H8v-2h8v2zm0-4H8v-2h8v2zm-3-5V3.5L18.5 9H13z"/></svg></div>
            Renewal drafting
          </li>
          <li>
            <div class="pain-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M20 4H4c-1.1 0-1.99.9-1.99 2L2 18c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h16c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V6c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm0 4l-8 5-8-5V6l8 5 8-5v2z"/></svg></div>
            Carrier email summarization
          </li>
          <li>
            <div class="pain-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M22 5.72l-4.6-3.86-1.29 1.53 4.6 3.86L22 5.72zM7.88 3.39L6.6 1.86 2 5.71l1.29 1.53 4.59-3.85zM12.5 8H11v6l4.75 2.85.75-1.23-4-2.37V8zM12 4c-4.97 0-9 4.03-9 9s4.03 9 9 9 9-4.03 9-9-4.03-9-9-9zm0 16c-3.87 0-7-3.13-7-7s3.13-7 7-7 7 3.13 7 7-3.13 7-7 7z"/></svg></div>
            Service request routing
          </li>
          <li>
            <div class="pain-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M11.8 10.9c-2.27-.59-3-1.2-3-2.15 0-1.09 1.01-1.85 2.7-1.85 1.78 0 2.44.85 2.5 2.1h2.21c-.07-1.72-1.12-3.3-3.21-3.81V3h-3v2.16c-1.94.42-3.5 1.68-3.5 3.61 0 2.31 1.91 3.46 4.7 4.13 2.5.6 3 1.48 3 2.41 0 .69-.49 1.79-2.7 1.79-2.06 0-2.87-.92-2.98-2.1h-2.2c.12 2.19 1.76 3.42 3.68 3.83V21h3v-2.15c1.95-.37 3.5-1.5 3.5-3.55 0-2.84-2.43-3.81-4.7-4.4z"/></svg></div>
            Commission automation
          </li>
          <li>
            <div class="pain-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M8 16h8v2H8zm0-4h8v2H8zm6-10H6c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2v16c0 1.1.89 2 1.99 2H18c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V8l-6-6zm4 18H6V4h7v5h5v11z"/></svg></div>
            Document generation
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="truth-callout fade-up">
        <h3>AI should reduce workload &mdash; not create complexity.</h3>
        <p>The agencies getting results from AI aren't chasing trends. They're automating the repetitive tasks that drain their team daily.</p>
        <div class="callout-visual">
          <div class="time-block">
            <div class="time-icon manual"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M11.99 2C6.47 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.47 10 9.99 10C17.52 22 22 17.52 22 12S17.52 2 11.99 2zM12 20c-4.42 0-8-3.58-8-8s3.58-8 8-8 8 3.58 8 8-3.58 8-8 8zm.5-13H11v6l5.25 3.15.75-1.23-4.5-2.67z"/></svg></div>
            <span>Manual work</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flow-arrow"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M16.01 11H4v2h12.01v3L20 12l-3.99-4z"/></svg></div>
          <div class="time-block">
            <div class="time-icon ai"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M21 10.5h-1.06C19.71 7.39 17.11 5 14 5c-1.07 0-2.07.25-2.97.69L12.55 7.2A5.5 5.5 0 0 1 14 7c2.62 0 4.75 2.06 4.94 4.65l.01.35H21l-3.5 4.5L14 12h2.5a3.001 3.001 0 0 0-5.95-.49l-1.81-1.6A5 5 0 0 1 14 7c.87 0 1.7.22 2.43.61L14.97 5.7C14.03 5.25 13.04 5 12 5 8.13 5 5 8.13 5 12h2.5l-3.5 4.5L.5 12H3a9 9 0 0 1 18 0h.5l-3.5-4.5L21 12v-1.5z"/></svg></div>
            <span>AI automates</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flow-arrow"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M16.01 11H4v2h12.01v3L20 12l-3.99-4z"/></svg></div>
          <div class="time-block">
            <div class="time-icon result"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-2 15l-5-5 1.41-1.41L10 14.17l7.59-7.59L19 8l-9 9z"/></svg></div>
            <span>Team freed up</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .truth-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 60px;
    align-items: start;
    margin-top: 48px;
  }

  .truth-left p {
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .truth-left p:first-child {
    font-size: 20px;
    color: var(--text);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .pain-list {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
    margin: 24px 0;
  }

  .pain-list li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 14px;
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .pain-icon {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 28px;
    height: 28px;
    background: rgba(244, 128, 33, 0.1);
    border-radius: 6px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-top: 1px;
  }

  .pain-icon svg {
    width: 14px;
    height: 14px;
    fill: var(--orange);
  }

  .truth-callout {
    background: var(--light-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 40px;
    border-left: 4px solid var(--orange);
  }

  .truth-callout h3 {
    font-size: 24px;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--charcoal);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .truth-callout p {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--text-light);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .callout-visual {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-top: 32px;
    padding-top: 28px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .time-block {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    text-align: center;
    flex: 1;
  }

  .time-icon {
    width: 44px;
    height: 44px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .time-icon svg { width: 22px; height: 22px; }
  .time-icon.manual { background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.15); }
  .time-icon.manual svg { fill: #ef4444; }
  .time-icon.ai { background: rgba(41, 63, 80, 0.12); }
  .time-icon.ai svg { fill: var(--blue); }
  .time-icon.result { background: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.15); }
  .time-icon.result svg { fill: #22c55e; }

  .time-block span {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-light);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }

  .flow-arrow svg {
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    fill: #d1d5db;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .truth-content {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 40px;
    }
    .callout-visual {
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
  }
</style>
